data.text:
We aim to unite and connect Wellington’s Rainbow Sport and Recreation Groups

We maintain a list of Sport and Recreation Clubs, and we also coordinate some events

We usually run a stall at the Pride Festival Fair every year

We are very grateful to Rainbow Wellington, Wellington’s Rainbow community networking group, for their financial support
